            <asp:HyperLink ID="HyperLink8" runat="server" Font-Size="X-Large">In the Indian state of Karnataka, there is a state-owned road transportation firm called Karnataka State Road Transport Corporation (Karnataka SRTC). The state of Karnataka owns it outright, provides connections with the rest of the state, Tamil Nadu, Kerala, Telangana, Andhra Pradesh, Maharashtra, Goa, and Puducherry Union Territory as well as routes to cities in southern Karnataka.</asp:HyperLink>
